::Astroblast/Drag Strip/Rippersnapper/Switchblade::

Rippersnapper arrives at the base, after sitting near the cave, 
gnawing on a piece of Symphony. &quot;What Rippersnapper miss? 
Rippersnapper RIP!&quot;

Drag Strip and Astroblast, in awe of what has happened, rush up to 
Megatron, and raise him above their heads, &quot;Hail Megatron, Hail 
Destruction!&quot;

Switchblade carries Condor back to base. When he arrives he 
instantly understands what has happened, plus he hears the 
chanting. &quot;Well well one falls just so another can take his place.&quot; 
He smiles thoughtfully. &quot;Megatron will be please to know that we 
now have two prisoners.&quot; He sets Condor down, and cheers, 
though he doesn&#39;t really care.


